text: Adina-Gina Rognean (born 28 May 1994) is a Romanian footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Romania women's national team. ==Career== Rognean has been capped for the Romania national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian women's footballers Category:Romania women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
